"<i><ref dst='weaponspecial_drains'>drains</ref></i>."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:123
msgid "Blizzard"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:125
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to <i><ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_slows'>slow</ref></i> enemy units and freeze terrain in a "
"3-hex radius."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:133
msgid "Counterspell"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:135
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 XP</span> to <i>disallow <ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref> attacks</i> in a 3-hex radius, "
"until cancelled.\n"
"          Disables Delfador’s spells, but not his passive skills."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:143
msgid "Polymorph"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:145
msgid ""
"Transform into a <ref dst='unit_Frost Stoat Poly'>stoat</ref> (<span "
"color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>1 XP</span>), <ref dst='unit_Cave Bear "
"Poly'>bear</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8 XP</span>), <ref "
"dst='unit_Giant Crab'>crab</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 "
"XP</span>), or <ref dst='unit_Roc'>roc</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' "
"style='italic'>32 XP</span>). Lasts until cancelled.\n"
"           Replaces Delfador’s attacks, spells, and passives, but does not "
"affect hitpoints."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:157
msgid "Glamour"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:159
msgid "Gain the <i><ref dst='ability_leadership'>leadership</ref></i> ability."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:173
msgid ""
"Ranged 12x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:180
msgid "Dancing Daggers"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:182
msgid ""
"Ranged 5x8 blade, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_backstab'>backstab</ref></i>"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:189
msgid "Enthrall"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:191
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to magically disguise "
"yourself as an awe-inspiring drake.\n"
"          Enemies in a 2-hex radius suffer a -10% penalty to both their "
"terrain defense\n"
"          (chance to evade) and chance to hit (except for magical attacks). "
"Lasts until cancelled."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:199
msgid "Animate Fire"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:201
msgid ""
"Learn to recruit <i><ref dst='unit_Fire Guardian'>Fire Guardians</ref></i>. "
"Fire Guardians gain +100% damage and XP\n"
"               while adjacent to you, but dissipate at the end of each "
"scenario."
msgstr ""

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:208
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:396
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1772
msgid "Contingency"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:210
msgid ""
"Whenever one of your human soldiers dies, they are instead returned safely "
"to your recall list."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:224
msgid ""
"Ranged 18x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:231
msgid "Chain Lightning"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:233
msgid ""
"Ranged 14x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>. If "
"this attack kills an enemy, you may attack again."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:240
msgid "Time Dilation"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:242
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 XP</span> to grant yourself "
"and all allies double movement and a second attack this turn.\n"
"          When this turn ends, affected units become <ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_slows'>slowed</ref>."
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:250
msgid "Cataclysm"
msgstr ""

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:252
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>99 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to blast everything in a 5-"
"hex radius. Units (except Delfador) will be reduced\n"
"          to 1 HP. Dries water, melts snow, burns forest, and levels castles/"
"villages."
msgstr ""

