msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. notice that appears at the beginning of the scenario if you select Deadly difficulty
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:162
msgid ""
"NOTE: ‘Deadly’ difficulty is intended to be a frighteningly difficult "
"challenge even for experienced players! If you’re new to Wesnoth, I strongly "
"suggest trying a lower difficulty."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. notice that appears at the beginning of the scenario if you select Hard difficulty
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:169
msgid ""
"NOTE: ‘Hard’ difficulty is intended to be a serious challenge even for "
"experienced players! If you’re new to Wesnoth, you may want to try a lower "
"difficulty."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. the fire wraiths are not visible yet. Delfador is about to appear on the left edge of the map
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:178
#, fuzzy
msgid "Faster, faster! The wraiths will soon be upon you!"
msgstr "Hâtez-vous, vite ! Les apparitions vont bientôt fondre sur vous !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. referencing events that happened minutes before the beginning of the campaign
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:193
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hey, how was I supposed to know the halfway cave was warded! All I did was "
"throw a few celebratory firebolts! For the spectators, you know?"
msgstr ""
"Hé, comment étais-je censé savoir que la grotte à mi-parcours était protégée "
"par des enchantements ? J’ai juste lancé quelques boules de feu pour fêter "
"ça ! Pour le public, vous voyiez?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. there's a blue orb at the east edge of the map, which will dispel the fire guardians that will soon appear to chase Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:198
#, fuzzy
msgid "Just hurry and get to the dispel orb!"
msgstr "Dépêche-toi d'atteindre l’orbe de dissipation !"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:206
#, fuzzy
msgid "Reach the blue orb at the east edge of the map"
msgstr "Atteindre l’orbe bleue à l’extrémité est de la carte"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. Delfador is currently just named "apprentice". He doesn't get his name until scenario 2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:211
msgid "Death of the Apprentice"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. this tells the player that 1) Delfador is Methor's apprentice, and 2) Delfador is very reckless
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:229
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Out of all the masters in Alduin, why did the sages curse me with the most "
"reckless apprentice in all Wesnoth?"
msgstr ""
"Parmi tous les maîtres d’Alduin, pourquoi a t'il fallu que les sages me "
"collent l’apprenti le plus téméraire de tout Wesnoth ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. this line is spoken as soon as the fire guardians enter the map
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:246
#, fuzzy
msgid "The wraiths are catching up! Keep moving!"
msgstr "Les apparitions te rattrapent ! Ne t'arrête pas !"

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#. another of Delfador's instructors; implying Delfador has attempted to firebolt the fire guardians before, and it ended badly
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:251
#, fuzzy
msgid "10 copper says he tries to firebolt them again..."
msgstr ""
"Je parie 10 pièces de cuivre qu’il va encore leur lancer une boule de feu…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Levitate is one of many spells that Delfador will have access to throughout this scenario. It grants him flight and skirmisher, which
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:256
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ignore her. You’re making good time so far — now cast Levitate and slip past "
"the eyestalks! You may need to cast it several turns in a row to keep ahead "
"of the wraiths."
msgstr ""
"Ne fais pas attention à elle. Tu avances bien pour l’instant — lance "
"Lévitation et glisse-toi entre les tiges oculaires ! Il faudra sans doute "
"enchaîner plusieurs invocations pour garder de l’avance sur les apparitions."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:260
#, fuzzy
msgid "Levitate? Master, are you sure?"
msgstr "Lévitation ? Maître, vous en êtes sûr ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:264
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh for the love of— remember what happened last time you tried to fight? "
"Just do it!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, pour l’amour du ciel… tu te souviens de ce qui s’est passé la dernière "
"fois que tu as essayé de te battre ? Fais-le, point final !"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:269
#, fuzzy
msgid "Casting Spells:"
msgstr "Lancer des sorts :"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:270
#, fuzzy
msgid "Double- or right-click on the apprentice to cast spells."
msgstr ""
"Double-cliquez ou faites un clic droit sur l’apprenti pour lancer des sorts."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. spoken after Delfador attacks the fire guardians, referencing the "10 copper" bet from earlier. Since there are 3 guardians and they have 50% fire resistance, this is not a wise move by Delfador.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:287
msgid "All right, all right! It’s just as you said."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:292
msgid "10 more copper for me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:305
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So he does know proper magic after all. It only took four failed exams..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, donc il sait faire un peu de magie finalement… … ça lui aura pris quand "
"même quatre examens ratés…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. if the levitate spell ends over impassable terrain (like lava), Delfador dies
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:319
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Almost there! Just fly across the chasm and touch the orb — and make sure "
"your levitate spell doesn’t end over lava!"
msgstr ""
"On y est presque ! Survole le gouffre et touche l’orbe — et veille à ce que "
"ton sort de Lévitation ne se termine pas au-dessus de la lave !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:333
msgid "Hello, my adoring fans!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mirya
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:337
msgid "Hey, what’re you doing! This isn’t the normal route!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Rolyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:341
msgid "We’d better get out of here. Remember what happened on his last exam?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just reached the end of the obstacle course / final exam (and the end of the scenario0
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:460
#, fuzzy
msgid "Yes! I’ve made it! This time has to be good enough."
msgstr "Oui ! J’y suis arrivé! Cette fois, ça devrait être suffisant."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:465
#, fuzzy
msgid "Well, what do you think?"
msgstr "Alors, qu’est ce que vous en pensez ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:471
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I say no. A mage needs wisdom; this apprentice cares only for his own "
"amusement. This one is a petty magician, not a wise sage or advisor of kings."
msgstr ""
"Je dis non. Un mage a besoin de sagesse ; cet apprenti ne pense qu'à "
"s’amuser. Ce n’est qu’un magicien insignifiant, pas un sage avisé capable de "
"conseiller des rois."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:475
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I say yes. I admit my apprentice enjoys the spotlight more than most, but "
"with this much magical aptitude who wouldn’t want to show off?"
msgstr ""
"Je dis oui. Je reconnais que mon apprenti cherche davantage à briller que la "
"moyenne, mais avec un tel don pour la magie, qui ne voudrait pas le montrer ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:479
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I think it’s obvious this is one of the most gifted magi we’ve trained in "
"years. The skill is innate; the wisdom will come with time."
msgstr ""
"Je pense qu’il est évident qu’il s’agit de l’un des magiciens les plus doués "
"que nous ayons formés depuis des années. Le talent est inné ; la sagesse "
"viendra avec le temps."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:484
#, fuzzy
msgid "So mine is the deciding vote. Very well, I’ve made up my mind."
msgstr ""
"Donc mon vote va permettre de trancher. Très bien, ma décision est prise."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. non sequitur. The screen has faded to black, and Delfador is hearing a voice with no apparent origin. In scenario 4, this is later revealed to be the elvish seer Elende, prophesying about Delfador's future.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:511
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>The Deceiver weaves the twine encircling the puppets in the court of "
"royals.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Le Trompeur tisse les fils qui enserrent les marionnettes de la cour "
"royale.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:515
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>Fatherless prince and sovereignless king, the balance of man hangs upon "
"this thread.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Prince orphelin et roi sans trône, le destin de l’humanité repose sur ce "
"fil.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:519
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>Should force and fire brandish themselves where wisdom and pity are left "
"wanting, this string of fate shall inexorably be sundered.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Si la force et les flammes s’imposent là où la sagesse et la pitié font "
"défau, ce fil du destin sera inexorablement brisé.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#. the screen has faded back to normal, and master Leollyn is annoyed that Delfador wasn't paying attention
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:532
#, fuzzy
msgid "Apprentice! Are you listening? I’m trying to congratulate you!"
msgstr ""
"Apprenti ! Tu m’écoutes au moins ? Je suis en train de te féliciter, bon "
"sang !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:536
#, fuzzy
msgid "But who— what— um, yes, I must have drifted off."
msgstr "Mais qui… quoi… euh… oui, j’ai dû perdre le fil un instant."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:540
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...as I was saying... apprentice, congratulations on your successful "
"completion of the practical portion of your graduation exam! Now we proceed "
"to the written section; please conjure your quill and parchment..."
msgstr ""
"…pour en revenir à ce que je disais… apprenti, toutes mes félicitations pour "
"avoir réussi la partie pratique de ton examen de fin d’études ! Passons "
"maintenant à la partie écrite : invoque ta plume et ton parchemin…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just taken lethal damage
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:559
msgid "Oh no! Master, help!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor casts a spell to save Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:564
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’ll save you!"
msgstr "Je vais te sauver !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:579
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(sigh) Not again! I suppose you’ll have to retry the exam next year... for "
"the sixth time."
msgstr ""
"(soupir) Pas encore ! Eh bien, il faudra que tu rapasses l’examen l’an "
"prochain… pour la sixième fois."

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:8
msgid "Stirrings of War"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:26
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the year 481 after the founding of Wesnoth, King Garard the Second grew "
"discontent."
msgstr ""
"En l’an 481 après la fondation de Wesnoth, le roi Garard II commença à "
"manifester son mécontentement."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:29
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With the Estmarks secured and the southern bandits pacified, his empire had "
"grown large and powerful. Garard’s marriage to the young Asheviere had "
"secured him a queen, as well as the promise of an heir. Yet despite these "
"achievements, the restless king could find no peace."
msgstr ""
"Avec la Marche de l'Est sécurisée et les bandits du sud pacifiés, son empire "
"était devenu vaste et puissant. Le mariage de Garard avec la jeune Asheviere "
"lui avait apporté une reine, ainsi que la promesse d’un héritier. Pourtant, "
"malgré ces accomplissements, le roi tourmenté ne trouvait aucune paix."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:33
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The king’s love lay in sword and shield, in battle and blood. Dissatisfied "
"with a life of languor among the estates of Weldyn, Garard looked instead to "
"the orcs of the Heart Mountains, whose raids had long been a nuisance across "
"his northern border."
msgstr ""
"Le cœur du roi battait pour l’épée et le bouclier, pour la bataille et le "
"sang. Mécontent de la vie monotone au sein des domaines de Weldyn, Garard se "
"concentra sur les orcs du cœur des Montagnes dont les raids semaient depuis "
"longtemps le désordre le long de sa frontière septentrionale."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:37
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Eager to retaliate, the king sent messengers far and wide. He called to arms "
"an expeditionary force to cross the Great River and lay claim to orcish "
"lands; a great show of power to secure Wesnoth’s might."
msgstr ""
"Poussé par le désir de représailles, le roi envoya des messagers partout. Il "
"convoqua une force expéditionnaire pour franchir le Grand Fleuve et prendre "
"possession des terres orques ; un grand étalage de force destiné à affirmer "
"la puissance de Wesnoth."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:41
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One of these messengers rode to the venerable Academy of Magic on Alduin, "
"summoning a contingent of magi to support Garard’s endeavor. A particular "
"young apprentice was especially enthusiastic..."
msgstr ""
"L’un de ces messagers se rendit à la vénérable Académie de Magie d’Alduin, "
"convoquant un contingent de mages pour soutenir l’entreprise de Garard. Un "
"jeune apprenti en particulier se montra particulièrement enthousiaste…"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Grunt
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:66
msgid "Ozgob"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Grunt
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:71
msgid "Clan Whitefang"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:127
msgid "Weldyn"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:148
msgid "15 gold"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:148
#, fuzzy
msgid "Treasure! Looks like a previous victim of the goblins."
msgstr "Trésor ! Probablement celui d’une victime des gobelins."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:185
#, fuzzy
msgid "Are we there yet?"
msgstr "On y est bientôt ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. a "seeker spell" is a made-up word to describe some kind of spell that helps you find your way to a destination
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:190
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Nearer than the last time you asked, yet further than we will be the next. "
"Really apprentice, would it kill you to learn a proper seeker spell?"
msgstr ""
"Un peu plus près que la dernière fois que tu as demandé, mais encore loin de "
"là où nous serons la prochaine fois que tu demanderas. Franchement, "
"apprenti, ça te coûterait tant que ça d’apprendre un vrai sort de recherche ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has never met King Garard II, but rather idolizes him
#. "no need to be so glum" is echoed by Methor in S13x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:196
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There’s no need to be so glum, master. As the head of our delegation, you’ll "
"even get to counsel with the king himself! What I wouldn’t give for a chance "
"to prove myself to him..."
msgstr ""
"Pas besoin d’être si morose, maître. À la tête de notre délégation, vous "
"aurez même l’occasion de conseiller le roi en personne ! Que ne donnerais-je "
"pas pour avoir la chance de faire mes preuves devant lui…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:200
#, fuzzy
msgid "Do you hear that?"
msgstr "Tu entends ça ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:200
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quiet!"
msgstr "Silence !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. 'stragglers' refers to soldiers (like Delfador and Methor) who are joining Garard's war-camp, but are arriving late
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:210
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"“Kill the stragglers”, they says. “You’ll have our best warriors”, they "
"says. N’ all I get are a bunch o’ lousy goblins? Lousy lazy lying—"
msgstr ""
"« Tuez les traînards », qu’ils disent. « On vous envoie nos meilleurs "
"soldats », qu’ils disent. Et moi, tout ce que j’ai, c’est une bande de "
"gobelins minables  ? Minables , paresseux, menteurs…"

#. [message]: role=gobbo1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:215
#, fuzzy
msgid "They’re here, they’re here! Humans on the clan road!"
msgstr "Les voilà, les voilà ! Des humains sur la route du clan !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:219
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"—then grab your spear, you loathsome lout! Don’t let them link up with the "
"rest of their army!"
msgstr ""
"—Alors chope ta lance, crétin ! Ne les laisse pas rallier le reste de leur "
"armée !"

#. [message]: role=gobbo1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:223
#, fuzzy
msgid "No, no, no! No fight! I run away!"
msgstr "Non, non, non ! Pas de combat ! Moi, je me tire !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:230
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why you runtish, yellow—"
msgstr "Sale petit trouillard…"

#. [message]
#. multiple goblins are running away
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:237
#, fuzzy
msgid "Wait for me!"
msgstr "Attendez-moi !"

#. [message]: role=gobbo3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:241
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run away! Back to the swamp!"
msgstr "Fuyez ! Retournez vite dans le marais !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. Ozgob has just killed one of the fleeing goblins
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:249
#, fuzzy
msgid "I said FORM RANKS! Rousers, get these runts organized!"
msgstr ""
"J’ai dit : FORMEZ LES RANGS ! Meneurs, mettez ces avortons en formation !"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:253
