msgid "Vidrug"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:341
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At last, here we stand on the eve of battle! Remember the plan: General "
"Lionel, soften up the orcish warriors while my knights look for an opening; "
"Methor, command the camp in my absence — those goblin raiders are still "
"being a nuisance."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, nous voilà à la veille de la bataille ! Souvenez-vous du plan : "
"Général Lionel, affaiblissez les guerriers orques tandis que mes chevaliers "
"cherchent une faille ; Methor, dirigez le camp en mon absence — ces pillards "
"gobelins continuent de poser problème."

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:348
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"M’lord, weren’ we waiting for the queen? Your wife had expressed an interest "
"in seeing an orc."
msgstr ""
"Mon seigneur, n’attendions‑nous pas la reine ? Votre épouse avait exprimé le "
"souhait de voir un orc."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:352
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We can brook no delay, Lionel. The opposing army is finally ready for "
"pitched battle. Ere dusk, my lance will be stained with orcish blood!"
msgstr ""
"Nous ne pouvons tolérer aucun retard, Lionel. L’armée ennemie est enfin "
"prête pour la bataille. Avant le crépuscule, ma lance sera teintée du sang "
"des orques !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:358
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This may prove a learning experience for you, apprentice. Keep your eyes "
"sharp as we guard the fort."
msgstr ""
"Cela pourrait être une expérience instructive pour toi, apprenti. Garde les "
"yeux ouverts pendant que nous gardons le fort."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:362
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The king commanded us to handle the goblins, master. We could do that by "
"guarding... or we could take a risk and assault the goblin camp."
msgstr ""
"Le roi nous a ordonné de nous occuper des gobelins, maître. Nous pourrions "
"le faire en gardant… ou en prenant le risque d'assaillir le camp gobelin."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:366
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know it’s not the caution you usually preach. But I want to be someone, "
"master, not just another wandering healer or village mage. Proving ourselves "
"to the king here could be the first step."
msgstr ""
"Je sais que ce n’est pas le genre de prudence que vous recommandez. Mais je "
"veux devenir quelqu’un, maître, pas juste un simple guérisseur errant ou un "
"mage de village. Faire ses preuves ici devant le roi pourrait être un "
"premier pas."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:370
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, young one, whatever shall I do with you... If you want to lead the "
"guards against the goblins I won’t stop you, but I’m afraid I can’t help you "
"either. My place is here, tending to the sick and injured."
msgstr ""
"Oh, jeune imprudent, que vais‑je faire de toi… Si tu veux mener les gardes "
"contre les gobelins, je ne te retiendrai pas, mais je ne pourrai pas "
"t’aider. Ma place est ici, à soigner les malades et les blessés."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:387
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:507
msgid "Defeat Khavur, the goblin leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:391
msgid ""
"Win before Garard defeats the orcish leader <span color='#ffffff' "
"size='small'>(probably turn 17 or 18)</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:395
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:521
msgid "Garard defeats Vidrug, the orcish leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:403
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:529
msgid "Death of Garard or Lionel"
msgstr ""

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:418
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:429
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:442
msgid "New Recruits:"
msgstr ""

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:419
msgid ""
"Methor is now a soldier in the royal army, and has access to Wesnoth’s full "
"roster of level 1 infantry. In addition to Mages, you can recruit Spearmen, "
"Bowmen, Fencers, and Heavy Infantrymen."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:431
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>If movement and combat are taking too long, you can enable “accelerated "
"speed” and “skip AI moves” in the Preferences menu.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Si les déplacements et les combats prennent trop de temps, vous pouvez "
"activer « Turbo » et « Sauter les déplacements de l’IA » dans le menu "
"Préférences.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:466
msgid ""
"We have some gold in camp, apprentice, and I am still in our keep and ready "
"to recruit. Remember to call for reinforcements if you need them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard's forces have just killed an orc
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:483
msgid "They fall before us!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. the player is attacking orcs instead of working towards the main scenario objective. This unlocks an alternate objective
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Apprentice, what are you doing! The king commanded us to engage the goblin "
"raiders, not the main orcish army!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:502
msgid ""
"Lighten up! What’s the worst that could happen? If I slay enough orcs in the "
"main battle, I’m sure the king won’t mind that I abandoned my post! ...right?"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#. $initial_orcs_remaining is between 8-15, $orcs_remaining is between 0-15
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:513
msgid ""
"Defeat at least $initial_orcs_remaining orcs ($orcs_remaining remaining)"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:517
msgid "Win before Garard defeats the orcish leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:525
msgid "Death of Delfador or Methor"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. a goblin has just attacked one of Garard's horsemen. Garard previously told Methor to guard against the goblins, but Delfador led the guards to battle instead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:545
msgid ""
"What the— who let all these runts in here! I should have known that healer "
"would be too soft-hearted to deal properly with the goblins."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador (or one of his troops) has killed another orc, and completed his alternate objective
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:572
msgid "Yes! We got another one!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:577
msgid "I’ve defeated so many orcs; surely the king must be impressed by now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Vidrug
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:582
msgid "Bah, filthy humans! This is hopeless. Whitefangs, retreat!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Khavur
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:598
#, fuzzy
msgid "Nooo! Help meeee..."
msgstr "Naaan ! Sauvez-moaaa…"

#. [message]: speaker=Vidrug
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:604
#, fuzzy
msgid "Bah, useless runts! This is hopeless. Whitefangs, retreat!"
msgstr ""
"Rien à faire avec ces bons à rien ! C’est foutu. Crocs-Blancs, retraite !"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:617
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, what’s this? Seems one of our young magi knows how to seize the "
"initiative."
msgstr ""
"Ah, que vois-je ? Il semble qu’un de nos jeunes magiciens sache prendre des "
"initiatives."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:621
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A proper war-mage is far too valuable to waste on the front lines; I may "
"have a special assignment for you. What’s your name, boy?"
msgstr ""
"Un mage de guerre digne de ce nom est trop précieux pour le front ; j’ai une "
"mission spéciale en tête pour toi. Comment t’appelles-tu, mon garçon ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. said by Delfador to himself (or maybe just thought in his mind)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:626
#, fuzzy
msgid "Commendation from the king himself! This is a dream come true."
msgstr "Une distinction du roi en personne ! C’est un rêve devenu réalité."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador is realy excited to go with the king, but deeply respects Methor and doesn't want to dissapoint him
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:631
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’d be honored, my lord! But I can’t give you my name — I’m just an "
"apprentice; Alduin has not yet assigned me one. And... I suppose I shouldn’t "
"want to leave without my master’s blessing..."
msgstr ""
"Ce serait un honneur, mon seigneur ! Mais je ne peux pas vous dire mon nom — "
"je ne suis qu’un apprenti, Alduin ne m’en a pas encore donné un. Et… je ne "
"devrais sans doute pas partir sans l’accord de mon maître…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:635
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By the traditions of our order, no apprentice shall venture alone; that "
"privilege is first awarded only to the journeymen!"
msgstr ""
"Selon les traditions de notre ordre, aucun apprenti ne doit aller à "
"l’aventure seul ; ce privilège est réservé en premier lieu aux compagnons !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:639
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...but apprentice, truth be told, you’ve had a journeyman’s skill for quite "
"some time now. I was hoping to impart a little more wisdom before advancing "
"you, but now I understand that fate has other plans."
msgstr ""
"…mais apprenti, en vérité, tu as depuis longtemps le niveau d’un compagnon. "
"J’espérais t’enseigner encore un peu de sagesse avant de te promouvoir, mais "
"il semble maintenant que le destin en ait décidé autrement."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. nonsense words, sounding magical, copied from the original DM
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:672
#, fuzzy
msgid "Thorum restro targa thorum..."
msgstr "Thorum restro targa thorum..."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. referencing the "Provost of the Council of Archmagi" mentioned by Delfador in HttT
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:692
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The light waxes bright. By the power of the high provost and the blessing of "
"the five sages, I declare you to be nameless NO LONGER!"
msgstr ""
"La lumière s’intensifie. Par le pouvoir du grand prévôt et la bénédiction "
"des cinq sages, je déclare que tu n’es plus sans nom !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:697
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i><b>DELFADOR</b></i> you shall be, and Delfador shall be YOU."
msgstr "<i><b>DELFADOR</b></i> tu seras, et Delfador sera toi."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:705
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, open your eyes. And OPEN THEM AGAIN!\n"
"\n"
"I grieve for the apprentice I have lost, but I celebrate the journeyman "
"Wesnoth has gained. Your naming ceremony is complete."
msgstr ""
"Delfador, ouvre les yeux. Et OUVRE-LES À NOUVEAU !\n"
"\n"
"Je déplore l’apprenti que j’ai perdu, mais je me réjouisdu compagnon que "
"Wesnoth a gagné. Ta cérémonie de nomination est terminée."

#. [unit]
#. [event]
#. [side]
#. [unit]: type={TYPE}
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:724
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1653
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1688
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1749
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1779
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:307
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:20
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1014
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:361
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1169
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:13
msgid "Delfador"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:733
#, fuzzy
msgid "Del-fa-dor; Delfador! Thanks master, I like the sound of that."
msgstr "Del‑fa‑dor… Delfador ! Merci, maître ! Ce nom a une belle résonance."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:737
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now farewell, Delfador, my ambitious young friend. If this is what you truly "
"want, I would never stand in your way. May we meet again in more peaceful "
"times."
msgstr ""
"Maintenant, adieu, Delfador, mon jeune ami plein d’ambition. Si c’est ce que "
"tu veux vraiment, je ne t’empêcherai jamais d’avancer. Que nos chemins se "
"croisent de nouveau en des jours plus paisibles."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:741
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yes, yes, well done to you both. Now that that’s settled, “Delfador”, it’s "
"time to pack your bags. You have a long journey ahead of you!"
msgstr ""
"Oui, oui, félicitations à vous deux. Tout étant désormais réglé, « Delfador "
"», il est temps de faire tes bagages. Un long périple t’attend !"

#. [message]: speaker=Vidrug
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:766
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:802
msgid "Bah... my kin will avenge me..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:772
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:808
msgid ""
"The first line of orcs is broken! Continue forth, riders; we ride to victory!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:777
msgid ""
"No; that’s not fair! I helped fight the orcs too; why is he going on without "
"me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:781
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:817
msgid "Now I’ll never impress the king..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:786
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:836
msgid "He’s going on without us! Now I’ll never impress the king..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has killed the orcish leader, but not killed enough orcs to impress Garard and complete his alternate objective
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:813
msgid ""
"No; that’s not fair! I struck the finishing blow; why is he going on without "
"me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:832
msgid ""
"The first line of orcs will soon be broken! Continue forth, riders; we ride "
"to victory!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:11
msgid "The Ambassador"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:43
msgid "Woses"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:113
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When King Garard spoke of a special mission for me, I hadn’t been expecting "
"something as quiet as messenger duty."
msgstr ""
"Quand le roi Garard a parlé d’une mission spéciale pour moi, je ne "
"m’attendais pas à quelque chose d’aussi tranquille que de servir de messager."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:115
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But I won’t disappoint him. I am to find Wesnoth’s ambassador to Lintanir "
"Forest, and then deliver to the elves a notice."
msgstr ""
"Mais je ne le décevrai pas. Je dois retrouver l’ambassadeur de Wesnoth pour "
"la Forêt de Lintanir, puis remettre aux elfes un message officiel."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:124
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The elvish border should be some distance northeast of here, through this "
"cluster of trees. The undergrowth is so thick... Perhaps this is an "
"opportunity to practice my new fire spell."
msgstr ""
"La frontière elfique devrait se trouver au nord-est d’ici, à travers ce "
"bosquet. Le sous-bois est si dense… Cela pourrait être l’occasion de tester "
"mon nouveau sort de feu."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:157
#, fuzzy
msgid "Eldebetam"
msgstr "Eldebetam"

#. [message]: speaker=leader2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:174
#, fuzzy
msgid "Boruroom! Burarum!"
msgstr "Boruroom! Burarum!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:178
#, fuzzy
msgid "What?! The tree speaks!"
msgstr "Qu’est ce que c'est ?! Un arbre qui parle !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:182
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’ve heard tell of tree-folk... you must be a wose! Err, I’m terribly sorry "
"for the fireball. I couldn’t tell you apart from an ordinary oak."
msgstr ""
"J’ai entendu parler de ces êtres-arbres… vous devez être un wose ! Euh, je "
"suis terriblement désolé pour la boule de feu. je ne vous avais pas reconnu, "
"je vous avais pris pour un simple chêne."

#. [message]: speaker=leader2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:186
#, fuzzy
msgid "Burarum! Boom-toom-hun-rum-tum-ala-lola-ala?"
msgstr "Burarum! Boom-toom-hun-rum-tum-ala-lola-ala?"

#. [message]: speaker=leader2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:190
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A-rumgur-gurmum-un-rumba-ala-burarum! Burarum-ala-bortum-untum! A-rumgur-"
"gurmum-un-rumba-ala-boruroom! BURARUM!!"
msgstr ""
"A-rumgur-gurmum-un-rumba-ala-burarum! Burarum-ala-bortum-untum! A-rumgur-"
"gurmum-un-rumba-ala-boruroom! BURARUM!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:194
#, fuzzy
msgid "It can’t understand me, and I can’t understand it... Oh no..."
msgstr "Il ne peut pas me comprendre, et je ne peux pas le comprendre… Oh non…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:210
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They’re preparing to attack! I’m not afraid of a few walking willows, but "
"burning down half the forest would hardly be the good first impression King "
"Garard tasked me with making."
msgstr ""
"Ils s’apprêtent à attaquer ! Quelques saules ambulants ne me font pas peur, "
"mais mettre le feu à la moitié de la forêt ne serait pas la meilleure "
"manière de faire bonne impression auprès du roi Garard."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:212
msgid ""
"I’m sure Methor would know what to do here. But I don’t. I think we have no "
"choice but to fight."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:220
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:224
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:407
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:910
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:364
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:558
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:624
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:178
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:476
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:425
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:648
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1040
msgid "Death of Delfador"
msgstr ""

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:241
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Woses have the <i>ambush</i> ability, making them invisible while in forest. "
"Any unit can temporarily reveal a wose by moving adjacent to it, but the "
"revealer will not be able to move afterwards — even if you have the "
"<i>skirmisher</i> ability. Ambushers will go back into hiding the moment you "
"move away (even if the ambusher hasn’t moved).\n"
"\n"
"Woses also have the powerful <i>regeneration</i> ability, and have high "
"resistance to several types of damage. <i><b>Make sure you recruit units "
"with effective damage types!</b></i> To see more details, right-click on a "
"wose and select <i>“Unit Type Description”.</i>"
msgstr ""
"Les woses possèdent la capacité <i>embuscade</i>, ce qui les rend invisibles "
"lorsqu’ils se trouvent en forêt. Toute unité peut temporairement révéler un "
"wose en se déplaçant à côté de lui, mais l’unité révélatrice ne pourra plus "
"se déplacer après — même si elle possède la capacité <i>tirailleur</i>. Les "
"woses reprennent immédiatement leur camouflage dès que vous vous éloignez "
"(même s’ils n’ont pas bougé).\n"
"\n"
"Les woses disposent également de la puissante capacité <i>régénération</i>, "
"et sont très résistants à plusieurs types de dégâts. <i><b>Assurez-vous de "
"recruter des unités infligeant des types de dégâts efficaces !</b></i> Pour "
"plus de détails, faites un clic droit sur un wose et sélectionnez <i>« "
"Description du type d’unité »</i>."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:255
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Where are those woses hiding? If I’m worried about my valuable veterans "
"getting ambushed, I could use new recruits as expendable pickets."
msgstr ""
"Où se cachent ces woses ? Si je crains que mes précieux vétérans ne soient "
"pris en embuscade, je pourrais recruter de la piétaille sacrifiable."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:295
msgid "This hollow tree is full of bats!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=leader2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:332
msgid "Ooohhhhoooom... Burarum..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:348
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Halt!! Who are you, and why do you trouble the trees of the Grey Grove? "
"Speak, strangers, for the wrath of Wesnoth and the Lintanir elves is upon "
"you!"
msgstr ""
"Halte !! Qui êtes-vous, et pourquoi troublez-vous les arbres du Bosquet "
"Gris ? Parlez, étrangers, car la colère de Wesnoth et des elfes de Lintanir "
"est sur vous !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:352
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Peace! Peace! You must be the man King Garard sent me to meet: Ambassador "
"Deoran."
msgstr ""
"Du calme ! Du calme ! Vous êtes sûrement l’homme que le roi Garard m’a "
"chargé de rencontrer : l’ambassadeur Deoran."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:360
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please, can you speak with these woses and tell them we’re not their "
"enemies? This whole battle has been a terrible misunderstanding."
msgstr ""
"S’il vous plaît, pouvez-vous parler à ces woses et leur dire que nous ne "
"sommes pas leurs ennemis ? Toute cette bataille n’est qu’un terrible "
"malentendu."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:364
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re a courier from Wesnoth? My apologies for the harsh words; long has it "
"been since Weldyn sent to this lonely post."
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes un messager de Wesnoth ? Veuillez excuser ma rudesse ; cela fait "
"longtemps que Weldyn n’a plus envoyé quelqu’un jusqu’à ce poste isolé."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:368
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But apology alone will not make right your transgressions against this rare "
"and precious wose-grove. If you really are who you claim to be, explain "
"yourself to me at once."
msgstr ""
"Mais de simples excuses ne suffiront pas à réparer vos torts envers ce rare "
"et précieux bosquet de woses. Si vous êtes bien celui que vous prétendez "
"être, justifiez-vous sans tarder."

#. [message]: speaker=leader2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Burarum! A-rumgur-gurmum-un-rumba-ala-burarum! Burarum-ala-bortum-untum! A-"
"rumgur-gurmum-un-rumba-ala-boruroom!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=young_wose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:396
msgid "Boom-toom-hun-rum-tum-ala-lola-ala! Burarum! Boruroom!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:400
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There’s more of them than I realized! And they’re really angry now! Even if "
"I could fight my way through, the elves would never trust me after such a "
"show of force..."
msgstr ""
"Il y en a bien plus que je n’avais imaginé ! Et ils sont vraiment furieux "
"maintenant ! Même si je parvenais à me frayer un chemin, les elfes ne me "
"feraient jamais plus confiance après une telle démonstration de force…"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:9
msgid "The Sylvan Seer"
msgstr ""

#. [time]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:13
msgid "Dusk"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:20
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"After a hasty explanation, and with Deoran’s aid, Delfador made many "
"apologies to the woses and their leader. Most of the destroyed trees had "
"fortunately not been killed, merely injured. Over the next several days, and "
"aided greatly by the woses’s natural regenerative abilities, Deoran showed "
"Delfador how to nurse the crippled tree-folk back to health."
msgstr ""
"Après une brève explication, et avec l’aide de Deoran, Delfador présenta de "
"sincères excuses aux woses et à leur chef. Heureusement, la plupart des "
"arbres touchés n’avaient pas été tués, seulement endommagés. Durant les "
"jours qui suivirent, et aidé par l’impressionnante capacité de régénération "
"des woses, Deoran enseigna à Delfador comment soigner ces êtres-arbres "
"meurtris et les ramener à la santé."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:22
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At last, relations mended, the two of them set out to deliver King Garard’s "
"message to the elves..."
msgstr ""
"Une fois les relations apaisées, tous deux partirent remettre le message du "
"roi Garard aux elfes…"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:48
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:53
#, fuzzy
msgid "Lintanir"
msgstr "Lintanir"

#. [unit]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:79
#, fuzzy
msgid "Eloreis"
msgstr "Eloreis"

#. [unit]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:91
#, fuzzy
msgid "Parandra"
msgstr "Parandra"

#. [unit]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:101
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1295
#, fuzzy
msgid "Kalenz"
msgstr "Kalenz"

#. [unit]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:111
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1311
#, fuzzy
msgid "Chantal"
msgstr "Chantal"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador is trying to speak, but gets interrupted by an elvish marshal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:176
#, fuzzy
msgid "Okay, yes, but—"
msgstr "Oui, d’accord, mais—"

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#. Delfador has brought a message from King Garard to the elves, asking them to attack the whitefang orcs
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:181
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I understand Weldyn’s stance on orcs, but Garard cannot change the facts: "
"our rangers have neither the training nor the elfpower to fight an offensive "
"war on open ground! What your king asks of us is impossible."
msgstr ""
"Je comprends la position de Weldyn concernant les orques, mais Garard ne "
"peut pas changer les faits : nos rôdeurs n’ont ni l’entraînement ni la "
"puissance elfique nécessaires pour mener une guerre offensive en terrain "
"découvert ! Ce que votre roi nous demande est impossible."

#. [message]: speaker=Parandra
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:185
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And why would we want to? The orcs stay out of our forests and we stay out "
"of their hills; this is the way things have been for over a century. Your "
"king promises us snow-covered mountains and barren desert as spoil, yet what "
"desire have we for more territory when Lintanir’s broad eaves could support "
"ten times our numbers?"
msgstr ""
"Et pourquoi le voudrions-nous ? Les orques restent hors de nos forêts et "
"nous restons hors de leurs collines ; les choses se passent ainsi depuis "
"plus d’un siècle. Votre roi nous promet des montagnes enneigées et des "
"déserts arides comme butin, mais quel désir aurions-nous de davantage de "
"territoires alors que les vastes forêts de Lintanir pourraient nourrir dix "
"fois notre population ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:189
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My honorable lords and ladies, I understand your duty to safeguard your "
"lands and your people. And is that not what Weldyn does now? King Garard "
"must know the orcs threaten all peoples of Wesnoth, or why else would he "
"wage this war?"
msgstr ""
"Honorables seigneurs et dames, je comprends votre devoir de protéger vos "
"terres et vos peuples. Et n’est-ce pas ce que fait déjà Weldyn ? Le roi "
"Garard doit savoir que les orques menacent tous les peuples de Wesnoth, "
"sinon pourquoi mènerait-il cette guerre ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:194
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You are, of course, welcome to scorn my King’s call; to loiter in Lintanir; "
"to live and laugh and <i>linger</i>, until Wesnoth’s strength is spent "
"towards a pyrrhic victory or a bloody defeat.\n"
"\n"
"But know that I shall answer my King’s summons; I shall march to war. In "
"honor of the friendship we have built over my many years here, I would hope "
"Lintanir will as well."
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes bien sûr libre de mépriser l’appel de mon roi ; de flâner à "
"Lintanir ; de vivre, rire et de <i>traîner</i>, jusqu’à ce que la force de "
"Wesnoth s’épuise dans une victoire à la pyrrhus ou une défaite sanglante.\n"
"\n"
"Mais sachez que je répondrai à l’appel de mon roi ; je marcherai à la "
"guerre. En l’honneur de l’amitié que nous avons bâtie au fil de mes "
"nombreuses années ici, j’ose espérer que Lintanir en fera de même."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:209
#, fuzzy
msgid "Truly, a moving speech..."
msgstr "Vraiment, un discours touchant..."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:213
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, I am sorry, but Eloreis is right. This is not our fight. I have long-"
"before seen the horrors of a war between elves and orcs, and have no desire "
"to plunge my people back into such a nightmare."
msgstr ""
"Deoran, je suis désolé, mais Eloreis a raison. Ce n’est pas notre combat. "
"J’ai depuis longtemps vu les horreurs d’une guerre entre elfes et orques, et "
"je n’ai aucune envie de replonger mon peuple dans un pareil cauchemar."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:217
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Should orcish hordes once again threaten the whole continent like they did "
"in times past, I would be the first to step up and offer my sword in service "
"of an alliance.\n"
"\n"
"But for territorial gain? I value your friendship and would honor the time "
"you have spent here, but if Wesnoth goes to war we cannot march alongside "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Si les hordes orques devaient de nouveau menacer tout le continent comme "
"jadis, je serais le premier à brandir mon épée au service d’une alliance.\n"
"\n"
"Mais pour un gain territorial ? J’accorde de la valeur à votre amitié et "
"honore le temps que vous avez passé ici, mais si Wesnoth entre en guerre, "
"nous ne pourrons pas nous joindre à vous."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#. 'Great-Grandfather' means Kalenz. Chantal is Kalenz's granddaughter
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:224
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Great-Grandfather, do not say such things! Deoran and his allies are risking "
"their lives in battle, and in all the vastness of Lintanir we can find "
"naught to offer but kind words? Force-of-arms is not the only strength of "
"the elves."
msgstr ""
"Arrière-grand-père, ne dites pas de telles choses ! Deoran et ses alliés "
"mettent leur vie en danger au combat, et dans toute l’étendue de Lintanir, "
"n’avons-nous rien d’autre à offrir que des paroles gentilles ? La force des "
"elfes ne se limite pas aux armes."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:228
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Chantal, sometimes you remind me so much of your grandmother... perhaps you "
"are right. I have seen too many friends fall during my unnaturally long "
"life; sometimes to battle, sometimes to age. I would postpone that fate for "
"Deoran if I can, for both your sakes."
msgstr ""
"Chantal, parfois tu me rappelles tellement ta grand-mère… peut-être as‑tu "
"raison. J’ai vu tomber trop d’amis au cours de ma vie anormalement longue ; "
"parfois à la guerre, parfois sous le poids de l’âge. Je tenterais de "
"retarder ce destin pour Deoran si je le peux, pour votre bien à tous les "
"deux."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:232
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, Delfador, what I now speak to you concerns one of our great secrets; "
"you are not to speak of this to anyone, even to your king."
msgstr ""
"Deoran, Delfador, ce que je m’apprête à vous révéler concerne l’un de nos "
"grands secrets ; vous ne devez le confier à personne, pas même à votre roi."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:237
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deep within Lintanir resides our sylph — an elven seer. We both favor and "
"fear Elende’s fractured, arcane sight; her strands of reflected prophecy. "
"Perhaps her visions may illuminate some measure of your futures, and in "
"doing so help you blaze brighter ones."
msgstr ""
"Au plus profond de Lintanir réside notre sylphide — une voyante elfe. Nous "
"craignons autant que nous admirons la vision fragmentée et magique d’Elende, "
"ses fils de prophétie réfléchie. Peut-être ses visions révéleront-elles une "
"part de votre avenir, vous aidant ainsi à en forger un plus radieux."

#. [message]: speaker=Eloreis
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:241
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Kalenz, are you sure this is wise? Seers are known to be... esoteric... and "
"Elende has been particularly cloistered these last few decades."
msgstr ""
"Kalenz, es-tu sûr que ce soit bien sage ? Les voyantes sont réputées pour "
"être… ésotériques… et Elende a été particulièrement recluse ces dernières "
"décennies."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:245
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I shall accompany them. I wish to spend some time with with these humans "
"before they depart."
msgstr ""
"Je vais les accompagner. J’aimerais passer un peu de temps avec ces humains "
"avant leur départ."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:249
#, fuzzy
msgid "And so do and so shall I. Come, follow me."
msgstr "Et moi aussi. Viens, suis-moi."

#. [time]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:268
msgid "Midnight"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:278
msgid ""
"There’s 5 gold pieces in this old boat! I suppose it’s better than nothing."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. said after a Forest Lion, Horned Scarab, or Silverback (a gorilla) attacks one of the player's units
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:359
#, fuzzy
msgid "Look out! There’re beasts in the forest!"
msgstr "Attention ! Il y a des bêtes dans la forêt !"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. said after the player double-clicks on Delfador to try and cast a spell
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:374
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No magic more unusual than a fireball, Delfador. We don’t want to appear "
"threatening."
msgstr ""
"Aucune magie plus inhabituelle qu'une boule de feu, Delfador. Nous ne "
"voulons pas paraître menaçants."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:393
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Kalenz leads Delfador, Deoran, and Chantal down a labyrinthine path through "
"the deep wood, past twists and turns and over winding tracks.\n"
"\n"
"In many places there is no path at all, and Delfador senses they are guided "
"more by the elves’ connection to the faerie than by conventional pathfinding."
msgstr ""
"Kalenz conduit Delfador, Deoran et Chantal à travers un sentier tortueux, "
"traversant les recoins mystérieux de la forêt profonde, où les pistes se "
"perdent dans les ombres des arbres.\n"
"\n"
"Par endroits, il n’y a même pas de vrai chemin, et Delfador ressent qu’ils "
"sont plus guidés par la connexion mystique des elfes aux esprits féériques "
"que par un simple sens de l’orientation."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:399
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The sun sets like a dying ember quenched beneath the horizon, and the forest "
"grows dim. Several times even Kalenz becomes lost, but each time manages to "
"find the way again. At last, in the dead of night, a small structure looms "
"out of the forest..."
msgstr ""
"Le soleil se couche comme une braise mourante éteinte sous l’horizon, et la "
"forêt s’assombrit peu à peu. Plusieurs fois, même Kalenz se perd, mais à "
"chaque fois il retrouve son chemin. Enfin, en pleine nuit, une petite "
"structure émerge de l’obscurité de la forêt..."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:409
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We have arrived. The seer’s mirror pool is just ahead; she herself should be "
"close by."
msgstr ""
"Nous sommes arrivés. La bassin miroir de la voyante est juste devant ; elle-"
"même devrait être tout près."

