#. [time]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1443
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1931
msgid "Dawn"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has missed the ending of the prophecy, and the player loses the scenario
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1467
#, fuzzy
msgid "I didn’t get to finish hearing everything..."
msgstr "Je n'ai pas pu tout entendre..."

#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Kalenz's mirror image), referencing Legend of Wesmere's invisibility potion and Landar
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1497
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Lich’s eye and brother’s bone; what have you sacrificed to save your people, "
"Kalenz? Your greatest fear stands before you... ahead of you?"
msgstr ""
"Œil du Liche et os du frère ; qu'as-tu sacrifié pour sauver ton peuple, "
"Kalenz ? Ta plus grande peur se dresse face à toi... ou plutôt, devant toi ?"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1501
#, fuzzy
msgid "That was long ago, Elende! This is about the humans’ story, not mine."
msgstr ""
"C'était il y a bien longtemps, Elende ! Il s'agit de l'histoire des humains, "
"pas de la mienne."

#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Deoran's mirror image), referencing his exile. I intend "nation" more in the "people" sense than the "country" sense.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1538
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran the exile returns home; returns to a nation that scorned him, ignored "
"his counsel and cast him away. What will become of the life he has built "
"amongst Lintanir’s twilight eaves?"
msgstr ""
"Deoran, l'exilé, revient chez lui ; il retourne dans une nation qui l'a "
"méprisé, ignoré ses conseils et rejeté. Que deviendra la vie qu'il a "
"construite parmi les franges crépusculaires de Lintanir ?"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1542
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know my duty! A captain of Wesnoth will never entertain doubts of loyalty, "
"whether to his country or his King."
msgstr ""
"Je sais quel est mon devoir ! Un capitaine de Wesnoth ne se permettra jamais "
"de douter de sa loyauté, que ce soit envers son royaume ou son roi."

#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Chantal's mirror image), referencing Cleodil's historic death and foreshadowing Deoran's upcoming death
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1555
#, fuzzy
msgid "Chantal—"
msgstr "Chantal—"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1559
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I already know what you’re going to say Elende! Don’t you dare; I will when "
"I’m ready."
msgstr ""
"Je sais déjà ce que tu t'apprêtes à dire, Elende ! Ne le tente pas ; je le "
"ferai quand le moment sera venu."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1565
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then you may soon understand some measure of your great-grandfather’s bygone "
"sorrows..."
msgstr ""
"Alors tu comprendras peut-être bientôt dans une certaine mesure les chagrins "
"passés de ton arrière-grand-père..."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1644
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1882
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1889
msgid "Elende"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. Elende reaveals that she's the one who gave the weird prophecy thing to Delfador at Alduin, even though she wasn't physically there
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1647
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And what of the fire mage? Young but ambitious, brilliant yet foolish. It "
"has been many moons since I spoke to you at Alduin."
msgstr ""
"Et le mage de feu, alors ? Jeune mais ambitieux, brillant mais imprudent. "
"Cela fait de nombreuses lunes que je ne t'ai pas parlé à Alduin."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1651
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That was you, back at graduation? I knew I heard a voice! Master Leollyn "
"thought I was going crazy..."
msgstr ""
"C'était toi, lors de la remise des diplômes ? Je savais que j'avais entendu "
"une voix ! Le maître Leollyn pensait que je perdais la tête..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1654
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1781
msgid ""
"Spend 8 XP to gain flight and the skirmisher ability until the start of your "
"next turn or until cancelled."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. pale spy meaning Asheviere. Referencing Asheviere resolving to kill Garard, and working with orcs to arrange the events of the next two scenarios
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1684
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I see secrets in the dark; a pale spy slips their bonds. A death, a "
"deceiver. Ringed swords, cold blood, false friends."
msgstr ""
"Je perçois des secrets dans l’obscurité ; un espion pâle se libérant de ses "
"entraves. Une mort, un trompeur. Épées encerclées, sang froid, faux amis."

#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's adventures in scenarios 8-10, where he works with (or kills) poachers to fight saurians, then fights undead and a ghost given the appearance of a living drake.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1745
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dark swamp looms. Purses and poachers, mirror and smoke. A figure of "
"shadow cloaked in the spirits of the dead. Battles won while wars are lost."
msgstr ""
"Le marais sombre se profile. Bourses et braconniers, miroir et fumée. Une "
"silhouette d’ombre enveloppée des esprits des morts. Des batailles gagnées "
"tandis que des guerres sont perdues"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1750
msgid ""
"Spend 16 XP to disallow magical attacks in a 3-hex radius, until cancelled."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. referencing the civil war when Asheviere takes power
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1775
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Brother against brother, father against child. From the barren throne will "
"rise an angel of ashes; both great and terrible alike. The delicate balance "
"of mankind will be broken, and flames shall blaze anew across the embers of "
"Haldric’s people."
msgstr ""
"Frère contre frère, père contre enfant. Du trône stérile s’élèvera un ange "
"de cendres ; grand et terrible à la fois. L'équilibre fragile de l’humanité "
"sera brisé, et des flammes s’enflammeront à nouveau sur les braises du "
"peuple de Haldric."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1780
msgid ""
"Spend 48 XP to grant yourself and all allies double movement and a second "
"attack this turn. When this turn ends, affected units become slowed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. referncing the future events of HttT; Konrad and Li'Sar retriving the sceptre of fire
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1871
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Black soot rains over Weldyn. The line of kings sundered; the ruby of the "
"wesfolk restored. The nameless son and the ashen daughter."
msgstr ""
"De la suie noire tombe sur Weldyn. La lignée des rois brisée ; le rubis des "
"wesfolk restauré. Le fils sans nom et la fille cendrée."

#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's choice in S10x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1885
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But this fate is not the only path. Mage of Alduin, you stand at a knot in "
"the strands, a nexus of the shards. For one brief moment, you will possess "
"the power to alter the currents of time; to rewrite the future that is "
"written."
msgstr ""
"Mais ce destin n'est pas le seul chemin. Mage d'Alduin, tu te trouves à "
"l’intersection des fils, un carrefour des éclats. Pendant un instant fugace, "
"tu détiendras le pouvoir d’altérer le cours du temps ; de réécrire l'avenir "
"qui est déjà tracé."

#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's choice in S10x. He can either listen to a drunk Garard and kill Garard's brother Arand based on false reports of a betrayal, or refuse, stay with Garard, and find out more about Arand before attacking
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1892
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When that moment comes, remember... endeavor to bestow not destruction with "
"that fire that you possess, but the gleaming light of truth instead. Quench "
"the flames of fear before all your world is consumed."
msgstr ""
"Quand ce moment viendra, souviens-toi... tente de ne pas répandre la "
"destruction avec ce feu que tu détiens, mais plutôt la lueur éclatante de la "
"vérité. Éteins les flammes de la peur avant que tout ton monde ne soit "
"consumé."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1896
#, fuzzy
msgid "But, what? I don’t understa—"
msgstr "Mais, quoi ? Je ne com—"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador previously said "But, what? I don’t understa—", but has now been kicked out of Elende's 'mirror world' and is back in the normal world. The scenario is over.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1953
#, fuzzy
msgid "—nd what you’re saying..."
msgstr "—prends pas ce que tu dis..."

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:10
msgid "The Deceiver"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador and his companions departed the mirror grove in hushed silence. The "
"Sylph’s words weighed heavily on each of their minds."
msgstr ""
"Delfador et ses compagnons quittèrent le bosquet des miroirs dans un silence "
"lourd. Les paroles de la Sylphide résonnaient dans leurs esprits, lourds de "
"sens."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:24
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"After lengthy deliberation, and much to Chantal’s displeasure, Delfador and "
"Deoran resolved to continue on with their mission. Exiting the forest after "
"several days’ westward travel, they soon sighted the banners of the king’s "
"army."
msgstr ""
"Après de longues délibérations, et bien à contre cœur de Chantal, Delfador "
"et Deoran décidèrent de poursuivre leur mission. Après plusieurs jours de "
"voyage vers l'ouest, ils sortirent enfin de la forêt et aperçurent bientôt "
"les bannières de l'armée du roi."

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:47
msgid "Shogro"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:61
msgid "Khovak"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:253
msgid "90 gold"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:253
#, fuzzy
msgid "These orcs were sitting on some gold! We can put it to better use."
msgstr ""
"Ces orcs étaient assis sur un véritable trésor ! Nous pouvons en faire un "
"meilleur usage."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:267
msgid "Captain Kestrel"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:315
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, are you sure you won’t reconsider staying in the Lintanir? What "
"Elende said..."
msgstr ""
"Deoran, tu es certain de ne pas vouloir rester à Lintanir ? Ce qu'Elende a "
"dit…"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:319
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My duty comes first, always. Would you truly want me any other way, Chantal?"
msgstr ""
"Mon devoir passe avant tout, toujours. Voudrais-tu vraiment qu’il en soit "
"autrement, Chantal ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#. referencing the beginning of HttT, where Delfador and Konrad are staying with the elves
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:325
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, it has been a pleasure to have you with us these years. And "
"Delfador, I hope to someday say the same of you as well. Elende seems to "
"think highly of you, and that means a great deal to me and my people.\n"
"\n"
"Should either of you ever find yourselves searching for a home away from "
"Wesnoth, you will always be welcome with us."
msgstr ""
"Deoran, cela a été un plaisir de t’avoir parmi nous pendant toutes ces "
"années. Et Delfador, j’espère qu’un jour je pourrai dire la même chose de "
"toi. Elende semble avoir une haute opinion de toi, et cela compte beaucoup "
"pour moi et mon peuple.\n"
"\n"
"Si l’un de vous deux venait un jour à chercher un refuge loin de Wesnoth, "
"vous serez toujours les bienvenus chez nous."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:341
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hail! The fledgling war-mage returns. Welcome, Delfador... and Deoran. Tell "
"me, are the north-elves with us?"
msgstr ""
"Salut ! Le jeune mage de guerre revient. Bienvenue, Delfador... et Deoran. "
"Dites-moi, les elfes du nord sont-ils avec nous ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:345
#, fuzzy
msgid "Deepest apologies my Lord, but they are not. Lintanir—"
msgstr ""
"Mes plus sincères excuses, mon Seigneur, mais ils ne sont pas avec nous. "
"Lintanir—"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:349
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I see. Unfortunate, but ultimately of no consequence. Victory is nearly won "
"even without their aid."
msgstr ""
"Je vois. C'est regrettable, mais finalement cela n’a aucune conséquence. La "
"victoire est presque acquise, même sans leur aide"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:354
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See there: we’ve driven the Whitefang chieftain and the last of his guards "
"into this old hill fort."
msgstr ""
"Regardez là-bas : nous avons repoussé le chef des Crocs--blancs et les "
"derniers de ses gardes dans cet ancien fort sur la colline."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:358
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The timing of your return couldn’t have been better, Delfador. General "
"Lionel and my brother Arand will press them from the front, while you sneak "
"in the back and roast their chief like a pig on a spit."
msgstr ""
"Ton retour ne pouvait pas tomber à un meilleur moment, Delfador. Le général "
"Lionel et mon frère Arand les attaqueront de front, pendant que toi, tu "
"passeras par l’arrière et rôtiras leur chef comme un cochon sur la broche."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:362
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Without their chief the Whitefangs will dissolve into an infighting mass of "
"petty squabbles, and our— Wesnoth’s victory will be complete!"
msgstr ""
"Sans leur chef, les Crocs--blancs se disloqueront dans des querelles "
"mesquines, et notre— la victoire de Wesnoth sera totale !"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:370
msgid "Defeat Khovak, the orcish warlord"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:374
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:523
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:483
msgid "Death of Delfador or Deoran"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:378
msgid "Death of Garard, Arand, Lionel, or Methor"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:399
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Don’t rush the assault, Lionel — no need to waste good men. Take some time "
"to stage our forces outside their walls, then attack just before the second "
"dawn."
msgstr ""
"Ne précipite pas l’attaque, Lionel — inutile de sacrifier de bons soldats. "
"Prends ton temps pour positionner nos forces à l'extérieur de leurs murs, "
"puis lance l’assaut juste avant la deuxième lueur de l’aube."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:403
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We have them right where we want them. Once our forces are assembled, I "
"shall join the battle personally and savor this victory up close."
msgstr ""
"Nous les avons coincés là où nous le souhaitions. Une fois nos forces "
"rassemblées, je prendrai part à la bataille personnellement et savourerai "
"cette victoire de près."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:407
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m surprised the Whitefangs have been driven to the brink of defeat so "
"quickly. Chantal speaks of them as numerous and cunning... I wonder if "
"something is amiss."
msgstr ""
"Je suis surpris que les Crocs-blancs aient été poussés si rapidement au bord "
"de la défaite. Chantal parle d’eux comme étant nombreux et rusés... Je me "
"demande si quelque chose ne clocherait pas."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:419
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An orcish shaman! On occasion I’ve known some of the other clans to use "
"their apprentices as warriors, but Clan Whitefang usually keeps theirs far "
"from the frontline."
msgstr ""
"Une chamane orc ! Il m’est arrivé de savoir que certains autres clans "
"utilisent leurs apprentis comme guerriers, mais le Clan Crocs-blancs garde "
"généralement les siens loin de la ligne de front."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:423
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What unusual magic! I don’t think I can tap into whatever fundamental forces "
"she was using, but now that I have her equipment I’ll bet I could figure out "
"how to imitate that draining attack... for our next battle, at least."
msgstr ""
"Quelle magie surprenante ! Je ne crois pas pouvoir accéder aux forces "
"fondamentales qu’elle utilisait, mais maintenant que j’ai son équipement, je "
"parie que je pourrais trouver comment imiter cette attaque drainante... pour "
"notre prochaine bataille, en tout cas."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:449
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I have still not recruited or recalled any soldiers! That orcish shaman we "
"defeated was standing on a keep. We should seize it and recruit our army "
"before we attack the orcs’ main camp."
msgstr ""
"Je n'ai toujours pas recruté ni rappelé de soldats ! La chamane orc que nous "
"avons défait se tenait sur un donjon. Nous devrions l'occuper et recruter "
"notre armée avant d'attaquer le camp principal des orcs."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:472
#, fuzzy
msgid "There’s more of them coming from the north! Should we go attack?"
msgstr "Il y en a d'autres qui viennent du nord ! Devons-nous attaquer ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Khovak
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:476
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stay in our fort, worm! Stick to the plan."
msgstr "Reste dans notre fort, vermine ! Tiens-t’en au plan."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. "trog" is a made-up slur referring to an orc
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:489
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re squatting in my summer home, trogs! No more raids for you; no more "
"pillage and plunder. Last chance to surrender!"
msgstr ""
"Vous occupez ma résidence d'été, bande de voyous ! Plus de raids, plus de "
"pillages ! C'est la dernière chance de se rendre !"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:493
#, fuzzy
msgid "Up yours, pink-skin!"
msgstr "Va te faire voir, blanc-bec!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador is telling his master Methor about the adventures he had in the last 2 scenarios
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:518
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hello there, master, it’s nice to see you again! You’ll never believe the "
"adventures I’ve had. Did you know there’s an elvish prophecy about me?!"
msgstr ""
"Bonjour maître, ça fait plaisir de vous revoir ! Vous ne devinerez jamais "
"les aventures que j'ai vécues. Saviez-vous qu'il existe une prophétie "
"elfique à mon sujet ?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:522
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(smiling) Delfador, don’t make me regret teaching you that psychedelic "
"spell! I’m just glad you’ve made it back safe and sound."
msgstr ""
"(souriant) Delfador, ne me fais pas regretter de t’avoir appris ce sort "
"psychédélique ! Je suis juste content que tu sois revenu sain et sauf."

#. [message]: speaker=Shogro
#. the whitefangs orcs are luring Garard into overextending. Shogro is bait, and has just died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:536
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stinking Ushka’e! This was a terrible plan..."
msgstr "Sale Ushka’e ! C'était un plan désastreux…"

#. [message]: speaker=Khovak
#. the whitefangs orcs are luring Garard into overextending. Khovak is bait, and has just died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:561
#, fuzzy
msgid "Human dogs! You’ve just sealed your deaths..."
msgstr "Chiens d’humain ! Vous avez scellé votre destin…"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:578
msgid "Run for the hills!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:593
#, fuzzy
msgid "Yes! Did I do well, Your Majesty?"
msgstr "Oui ! Ai-je bien agi, Sire ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard thinks he's won, even though he hasn't
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:598
#, fuzzy
msgid "Indeed you did. Fantastic battle, everyone, the orcs are broken!"
msgstr ""
"En effet, vous avez bien fait. Excellente bataille, tout le monde, les orcs "
"sont écrasés !"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:606
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Footmen — down into the fort’s dungeons! Flush out any stragglers and "
"complete our victory."
msgstr ""
"Fantassins — descendez dans les donjons du fort ! Éliminez les retardataires "
"et parachevez notre victoire."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard thinks he's won, even though he hasn't. "Wold" means "a piece of high, open, uncultivated land or moor."
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:650
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hah! I think “Garard’s Wold” will make a good name for the new province... "
"or perhaps “Garard’s Triumph”? What do you think, Lionel?"
msgstr ""
"Hah ! Je pense que « Les collines de Garard » sera un bon nom pour la "
"nouvelle province... ou peut-être « Le Triomphe de Garard » ? Qu'en penses-"
"tu, Lionel ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:655
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, something’s wrong. The orc leader we killed... isn’t the Whitefang "
"chief."
msgstr ""
"Delfador, il y a quelque chose qui cloche. Le chef orc que nous avons tué... "
"ce n'est pas le chef des Crocs-blancs."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:659
#, fuzzy
msgid "What? How can you tell?"
msgstr "Quoi ? Comment peux-tu en être sûr ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:663
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I met Clan Whitefang’s leaders around a year ago, when Lintanir negotiated a "
"treaty. This orc’s face is narrower than I remember, and his helmet doesn’t "
"have the right war-paint. Delfador, I think we’ve been tricked!"
msgstr ""
"J'ai rencontré les chefs du Clan Crocs-blancs il y a environ un an, quand "
"Lintanir a négocié un traité. Le visage de cet orc est plus étroit que celui "
"dont je me souviens, et son casque n'a pas les peintures de guerre "
"appropriées. Delfador, je pense qu'on nous a trompés !"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Are you even trying to fight, Delfador!? I should have known a mage would "
"never have the stomach for true battle; get back to Alduin where you belong!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:10
msgid "Ring of Swords"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:46
msgid "Ghazgir"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:59
msgid "Muhku"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:76
msgid "Irbirch"
msgstr "Irbirch"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:80
msgid "Blackcrest Orcs"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:88
msgid "Ssisaix"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:92
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:104
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:75
msgid "Blackcrest Saurians"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:100
msgid "Xairr"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:349
msgid "Chief Ushka'e"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. this is the whitefang chief. He's happy that Garard has walked into his trap
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:355
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You see? What did I tell you! Their king is nothing but a feeble-minded "
"goblin runt, who does exactly what I want. The trap is sprung! Now we crush "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Vous voyez ? Qu'est-ce que je vous avais dit ! Leur roi ne vaut pas mieux "
"qu'un gobelin faible d'esprit, il fait exactement ce que je veux. Le piège "
"est tendu ! Maintenant, on les écrase."

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. Irbirch is a representative of clan blackcrest, now (tenuously) allied with whitefang. The "spy" references Asheviere (probably; might be an agent of Iliah-Malal instead), who came up with the plan and told it to the orcs
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:377
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Bwahaha, when did you Whitefangs become so weak as to follow the ploy of a "
"spy? Blackcrest warriors would never have let humans advance so far into our "
"lands!"
msgstr ""
"Bwahaha, depuis quand les Crocs-blancs sont-ils devenus si faibles qu’ils "
"suivent les manigances d’un espion ? Les guerriers Crêtes-Noires n’auraient "
"jamais permis aux humains d’avancer aussi loin dans nos terres !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. referencing clan blackcrest's saurian allies.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:382
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your “warriors” only survive by cowering behind your slimy lizard allies! "
"But since Clan Blackcrest has begged so-like trembling goblins, Clan "
"Whitefang will agree to work together."
msgstr ""
"Vos « guerriers » ne survivent qu'en se barricadant derrière vos visqueux "
"alliés lézards ! Mais puisque le Clan Crêtes-Noires a supplié comme de "
"simples gobelins tremblants, le Clan Crocs-Blancs acceptera de collaborer "
"avec vous."

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. neither side has actually offered to work together. Subversive messengers poised as members of each clan and manipulated them into working together against Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:387
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Since WE begged!? YOU invited US here; your messenger was quaking in his "
"boots when he groveled before Chief Ghuvog asking for help!"
msgstr ""
"Parce que ce serait NOUS qui aurions supplié !? VOUS NOUS avez invités ici ; "
"votre messager tremblait de tous ses membres lorsqu'il s'est prosterné "
"devant le chef Ghuvog pour lui demander de l'aide !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:391
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What are you talking abo— Oh forget it, just make sure your clan does its "
"job! No human leaves this valley alive!"
msgstr ""
"De quoi parlez-vous ? Oh, laissez tomber, assurez-vous simplement que votre "
"clan fasse son travail ! Aucun humain ne sortira vivant de cette vallée !"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:411
msgid "Bazur"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Bazur
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:419
msgid "Lousy chief! Lousy plan! Next time I’m doing this on my own terms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard has just realized he's surrounded
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:437
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What devilry is this? How did they sneak in behind us. I’m separated from my "
"generals and most of my soldiers..."
msgstr ""
"Quelle infamie est-ce ? Comment ont-ils pu s'infiltrer derrière nos lignes ? "
"Je suis coupé de mes généraux et de la plupart de mes soldats…"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:441
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Foul orcs, come at me then! If this is where I am to fall, I shall make such "
"a stand as to stir the gods themselves to tears!"
msgstr ""
"Infâmes orques, venez donc à moi ! Si c'est là que je dois tomber, je me "
"battrai avec une telle force que les dieux eux-mêmes en auront les larmes "
"aux yeux !"

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. Asheviere is next to Irbirch. The player is led to think she's been captured, but it's possible she actually went of her own free will to escape Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:451
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Nice speech! I wonder what your wife thinks of it? Don’t worry, we’ll have "
"plenty of fun with her, <b><i>and</i></b> your unborn heir. Haw, haw, haw!"
msgstr ""
"Jolie tirade ! Je me demande ce que ta femme en pense ? Ne t'inquiète pas, "
"on va bien s'amuser avec elle, <b><i>et</i></b> ton futur héritier. Ha ha "
"ha !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:475
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(aghast) That’s— They’ve captured the queen! Asheviere’s no warrior, and "
"fragile with pregnancy. We have to rescue her!"
msgstr ""
"(Affolé) C’est… Ils ont capturé la reine ! Asheviere n’est pas une "
"guerrière, et sa grossesse la rend fragile. Il faut la secourir !"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:479
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Surrounded and absent the queen; this is a disaster! Quick, we must rally "
"what’s left of the crown’s infantry. Send a detachment to rescue Queen "
"Asheviere, and have the rest protect King Garard until Lionel and Arand can "
"break through to us!"
msgstr ""
"Encerclés et sans la reine ; c'est un désastre ! Vite, il faut rassembler ce "
"qu'il reste de l'infanterie du royale. Envoyez un détachement pour secourir "
"la Reine Asheviere, et le reste devra protéger le Roi Garard jusqu'à ce que "
"Lionel et Arand réussissent à percer jusqu'à nous !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:483
#, fuzzy
msgid "I won’t let you down! For Wesnoth!"
msgstr "Je ne vous laisserai pas tomber ! Pour Wesnoth !"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:490
msgid "Fail to rescue Asheviere before turns run out"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:493
#, fuzzy
msgid "Defeat Irbirch to recapture Asheviere, then survive until turns run out"
msgstr ""
"Vaincre Irbirch pour libérer Asheviere, puis survivre jusqu'à la fin des "
"tours."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:500
msgid "Survive until turns run out"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:527
msgid "Death of Garard, Asheviere, or Methor"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#. the player (and Garard) is still alive. The orcs and saurians expected them to die by now
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:588
#, fuzzy
msgid "They ssstill sssurvive! Thisss was not the plan!"
msgstr "Ils ont ssssurvécu ! Ce n'était pas prévu !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:592
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then send in more warriors and finish them off, you worthless Blackcrest "
"lizards! This is <b>our</b> homeland; our ranks swell by the hour, while "
"these humans dwindle every moment."
msgstr ""
"Alors envoyez plus de guerriers et finissez-en, misérables lézards des "
"Crêtes-noires ! C'est <b>notre</b> terre ; nos rangs grossissent d'heure en "
"heure, tandis que les rangs des humains se font de plus en plus clairsemés."

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:597
msgid ""
"Useless lizards! Can’t even keep themselves alive, much less win a war. Send "
"in more orcs! This is <b>our</b> homeland; our ranks swell by the hour, "
"while these humans dwindle every moment."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:610
#, fuzzy
msgid "They’re being reinforced!"
msgstr "Ils reçoivent des renforts !"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:649
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This alliance between races is a great ill fortune! I’ve oft known orcs to "
"recruit trolls, but seldom saurians. And with these three factions fighting "
"together, soon all the warlords will hear of their prowess."
msgstr ""
"Cette alliance entre races est une bien mauvaise nouvelle ! J'ai souvent vu "
"des orcs recruter des trolls, mais rarement des sauriens. Et avec ces trois "
"factions qui luttent ensemble, bientôt tous les seigneurs de guerre "
"entendront parler de leur bravoure."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:653
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It takes a great show of strength to unite the fractious orcs, but after "
"this disaster countless more will surely flock to the Blackcrest and "
"Whitefang banners. Orcs follow might above all else, even clan blood."
msgstr ""
"Il faut une grande démonstration de force pour unifier les factions orcs, "
"mais après ce désastre, des hordes viendront sans doute se rallier aux les "
"bannières des Crêtes-Noires et des Crocs-blancs. Les orcs suivent avant tout "
"la force, même avant les liens de sang de leur clan."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:657
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Utter madness, all of this! The orcish clans are a hornet’s nest that should "
"never have been kicked. Pillagers and raids we can deal with, but total war "
"is something else entirely."
msgstr ""
"Pure folie aue tout ça ! Les clans orcs sont un nid de frelons qu'on "
"n'aurait jamais dû déranger. Les pillards et les excursions, ça se gère, "
"mais la guerre totale, c’est une toute autre affaire."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:661
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quiet, both of you! If I wanted your advice I would have asked for it!"
msgstr ""
"Silence, tous les deux ! Si j'avais besoin de vos conseils, je vous les "
"aurais demandés !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. the player has just attacked the whitefang chief. He then flees
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:673
msgid "Worthless humans! You’ll never defeat me, or clan Whitefang!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:679
msgid "Coward! Stand and fight!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:694
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They sssneak off to the northeassst, towardsss their queen! Ssshould I "
"pursssue?"
msgstr ""
"Ils ssse faufilent vers le nord-essst, en direction de leur reine ! Dois-je "
"lesss poursuivre ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:698
#, fuzzy
msgid "Finish off their king, lizard! I’ll handle things here."
msgstr "Achève leur roi, lézard ! Je m'occupe du reste."

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:710
#, fuzzy
msgid "Come to ransom back your queen? Too bad, she’s mine!"
msgstr "Tu viens payer la rançon de ta reine ? Dommage, elle est à moi !"

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:714
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Maybe once she pops out her kid you can pay me double for both! Haw, haw, "
"haw."
msgstr ""
"Peut-être qu’une fois qu'elle aura pondu son gosse, tu pourras me payer le "
"double pour les deux ! Ha, ha, ha."

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. a representative of clan blackcrest has died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:726
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Great Chief Ghuvog will avenge me! Clan Blackcrest will never rest.. until "
"Wesnoth is... razed to... ash..."
msgstr ""
"Le Grand Chef Ghuvog me vengera ! Le Clan Crêtes-noires ne connaîtra jamais "
"le repos… jusqu’à ce que Wesnoth soit… réduite en cendres…"

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#. Asheviere tries to say something, but gets interrupted
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:739
msgid "Thank yo—"
msgstr "Merci à-"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. both Deoran and Garard talk over Asheviere. She doesn't get any agency of her own, even from Deoran (who generally stands up for her)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:744
#, fuzzy
msgid "Not now, milady! We have to get you out of here!"
msgstr "Pas maintenant, madame ! Il faut vous faire sortir d'ici d’abord!"

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#. asheviere tries to say something, but gets interrupted
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:754
#, fuzzy
msgid "Garard, I—"
msgstr "Garard, je—"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. both Deoran and Garard talk over Asheviere. She doesn't get any agency of her own, even from Deoran (who generally stands up for her)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:759
msgid "Not now, woman! I have a battle to fight!"
msgstr "Pas maintenant, femme ! J'ai un combat à mener !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ghazgir
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:772
msgid "I’m not dying! Just... need a moment..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mukhu
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:779
msgid "Nooo! Help meeee!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Xairr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:786
msgid "Ssssuch ssssskill!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:793
msgid "Cursessss, I am sssslain!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. Lionel appears with reinforcments to help Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:841
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Rally behind me, men! We swore our oaths, now we do our duty. Fight, fight "
"through to the king!"
msgstr ""
"Rassemblez-vous derrière moi, mes braves ! Nous avons prêté serment, "
"maintenant accomplissons notre devoir. Combattez, combattez jusqu’au roi !"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. the player has survived, but failed ot rescue the queen
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:860
msgid ""
"But the queen! If we leave her in the hands of the orcs she’ll surely be "
"tortured and killed!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:864
msgid "I’m sorry, there’s no time! We have to get the king out of here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:885
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sir, look out!"
msgstr "Sire, Gare à vous!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:900
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1384
msgid "<b><i>NNnrgh!</i></b>"
msgstr "<b><i>NNnrgh!</i></b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. Lionel has appeared with reinforcments to help Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:919
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By the Sceptre, I got here just in time! They caught us completely by "
"surprise. We’re holding a corridor but I don’t know for how long — we’ve got "
"to get you back to Fort Garard, sir."
msgstr ""
"Par le Sceptre, je suis arrivé juste à temps ! Ils nous ont complètement "
"surpris. On tient un passage, mais je ne sais pas combien de temps ça va "
"durer — il faut absolument vous ramener au Fort Garard, sire."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:923
#, fuzzy
msgid "Lionel! I’d almost feared this was the end."
msgstr "Lionel ! J'avais presque craint que ce ne soit la fin."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:936
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But how did this disaster happen? We were on the eve of victory! Did someone "
"betray our plans to the enemy? Or am I really just that predictable!?"
msgstr ""
"Mais comment ce désastre a-t-il pu se produire ? Nous étions si proches de "
"la victoire ! Est-ce que quelqu’un a trahi nos plans à l’ennemi ? Ou suis-je "
"vraiment aussi prévisible ?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:940
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Couldn’t tell you, m’lord. But there’ll be time to talk later. It looks like "
"this war is going to last a lot longer than we’d planned..."
msgstr ""
"Je ne pourrais pas vous dire, sire. Mais on aura du temps pour en parler "
"plus tard. On dirait que cette guerre va durer bien plus longtemps que "
"prévu..."

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:16
msgid "The Great River"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:41
msgid "Part II"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:47
msgid ""
"The entry of Clan Blackcrest into the war opens up a new front further west, "
"demanding swift response. Wesnoth fully mobilizes, and a series of bloody "
"battles at the Ford of Abez end in deadlock for both sides. The ford is "
"heavily fortified, and river commerce grinds to a halt. Many years pass, "
"with neither side able to gain an advantage."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:51
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, Asheviere gives birth to a healthy baby boy — the Crown Prince "
"Eldred. Under heavy pressure from both parents and via the tutelage of "
"General Lionel, Eldred rapidly matures into a princeling soldier. Prince "
"Arand takes Eldred under his wing, and working in tandem the uncle and "
"nephew are able to stabilize the eastern front around Fort Garard. Whitefang "
"orcs still firmly hold the hills, but limited settlement begins."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:55
msgid ""
"Delfador grows older, wiser, and significantly more powerful. He makes a "
"name for himself as the king’s premier war-mage, and quickly gains a "
"reputation as a ferocious fighter. His bold maneuvers break through orcish "
"lines several times at the Ford of Abez, but continually become stymied by "
"saurian reinforcements."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:59
msgid ""
"As Wesnoth’s casualties continue to mount, and with no end in sight, "
"Delfador decides to take matters into his own hands. The war-mage prepares a "
"force of mercenary northmen to sneak behind enemy lines and determine the "
"nature of Clan Blackcrest’s orc-saurian alliance..."
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:76
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:58
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:30
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:28
msgid "Delfador’s Hirelings"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Saurian Ambusher
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:88
